---
/**
 * AI 자동 생성 정보 섹션
 */
---

<section class="py-20 bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-900 via-pink-900 to-indigo-900">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">
        완전 자동화된 AI 연재 시스템
      </h2>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mt-12">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">🕐</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">매일 새벽 2시</h3>
          <p class="text-purple-200">정확한 시간에 자동으로 새로운 에피소드 업데이트</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">🤖</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">AI 자동 창작</h3>
          <p class="text-purple-200">AI가 완벽한 스토리 연속성으로 창작</p>
        </div>

        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-white/10 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <span class="text-2xl">⭐</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">품질 보장</h3>
          <p class="text-purple-200">7.5/10 이상의 품질을 자동으로 검증하고 보장</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>